author: Catherine Hanrahan
title: Confused about what to do about coronavirus? This data says just stay home
description: The success or failure of Australia's coronavirus fight relies to a remarkable degree on just one thing, new modelling has found.
content:

The success or failure of Australia's coronavirus fight relies to a remarkable degree on just one thing, new modelling has found.
And that thing is whether individual Australians now follow official advice and just stay home… [+7596 chars]
